title: VA - Gregorian Chants (Timeless Uplifting Performances) [FLAC]
description:
These hauntingly beautifully unaccompanied male voice performances have been used to evoke profound spirituality ever since their inception at the behest of Pope Gregory (hence "Gregorian") in the 8th century AD. This collection contains some of the best-known of all the chants, and is an ideal introduction to the cloistered world of sacred music.
